data.title: Vyborg starts work on Gazprom drilling rigs
data.meta_description: VYBORG Shipyard has started building the first of two semi-submersible drilling rigs that will be used by Gazprom to help develop the giant Shtokman gas-condensate field in the Russia side of the Barents Sea, writes Martyn Wingrove.
